Package: grateful
Title: Facilitate Citation of R Packages
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2018-11-09
Authors@R: c(person('Francisco', 'Rodriguez-Sanchez', email='f.rodriguez.sanc@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre')),
    person('Shaurita D.', 'Hutchins', role = c('ctb')))
Description: Facilitates citation of R packages used in analysis projects. 
    Scans project for packages used, get their preferred citation, and produces
    a document with citations in the preferred bibliography format, ready to be 
    pasted into reports or manuscripts bibliography list.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  checkpoint,
  rmarkdown,
  utils
Suggests: testthat
URL: https://github.com/Pakillo/grateful
BugReports: https://github.com/Pakillo/grateful/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
